### RESQID — Students List API Tests
### File: src/request/students.http
### =============================================================================

@baseUrl   = http://localhost:3000/api/school-admin
@token     = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..4U7bej-XYsVwVBagi6gy4HHb6fGIgZkZfY8CWa5rit4
@schoolId  = ee20bd32-c539-4489-ae22-ce35c4b24a7b	
@badUUID   = ee20bd32-c539-4489-ae22-ce35c4b24a8b

### =============================================================================
### ✅ HAPPY PATH
### =============================================================================

### [1] Default — page 1, 10 per page, no filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [2] Search by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?search=aarav
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Filter by class
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?class=Class 6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Filter by section
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?section=A
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [5] Filter by token status
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?token_status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [6] Combined filters — class + section + token status
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?class=Class 6&section=A&token_status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [7] Search + filter combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?search=sharma&class=Class 7&token_status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [8] Sort by class ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?sort_field=class&sort_dir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [9] Sort by joined date descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?sort_field=created_at&sort_dir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [10] Page 2 with limit 5
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?page=2&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [11] Max limit (100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### ❌ VALIDATION ERRORS — rejected at middleware, never hits DB
### =============================================================================

### [12] Missing auth — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students
Accept: application/json

###

### [13] Invalid schoolId format — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{badUUID}}/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [14] Wrong school (tenant mismatch) — expect 403 FORBIDDEN
GET {{baseUrl}}/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [15] Invalid token_status value — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
### (must be one of ACTIVE|UNASSIGNED|EXPIRED|REVOKED|ISSUED|INACTIVE)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?token_status=INVALID_STATUS
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [16] Invalid sort_field — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
### (whitelist: first_name|class|created_at only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?sort_field=password_hash
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [17] limit over 100 — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR (max is 100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?limit=999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [18] Search too long (over 100 chars) — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/students?search=aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###
